programme.desc: Pertama kali bertemu Inspektor Fahri Rakib, hati Hania berdetak kencang. Pelbagai cara dia cuba untuk dapatkan cinta Fahri. Rasa malu dan ego dibuang demi memiliki hati Fahri. Dalam mengelak, Fahri juga jatuh cinta pada guru yang menumpang sewa di kampungnya ini. Beberapa kali pertemuan yang dicipta Hania, akhirnya Fahri juga jatuh cinta pada Hania. Saat kasih bersulam, dugaan datang. Hania merasakan dirinya tidak dipedulikan. Saat hati Hania bersedih dengan sikap Fahri, ada jiwa yang sedang menunggu untuk kembali bermukim di hati. Dalam episod ini Fahri datang ke rumah keluarga Hania untuk berjumpa Hania yang sedang bercuti. Di kampung tersebar lagi fitnah tentang Cikgu Hania. Mak Raha syak Ila yang menyebar fitnah itu. Fahri telah membawa Hania melawat neneknya yang sakit di kampung. Fahri turut membawa Hania bercuti selepas itu. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Ali Reza, Dayang Areeda dan Alif Hadi.

Nazir telah membuat laporan polis tentang ugutan Hania itu. Pihak polis datang untuk menahan Hania untuk siasatan lanjut. Dalam pada masa yang sama ayah Hania sakit tenat. programme.title: Game Over Romeo Ep13
programme.desc: Black paksa Hany cakap di mana Tiya. Hany pun ceritakan hal yang sebenar. Black heret Hany cari Tiya di lereng-lereng bukit berdekatan tapi tidak ada. Bukit itu bahaya. Ramai yang jatuh dan hilang. Black tak percaya. Black gertak Hany tapi Hany tetap tak tahu di mana Tiya berada. Hany sendiri mahu cari Tiya untuk minta maaf. Dia dah insaf.

programme.title: Jodoh Warisan Tante
programme.desc: Jesie yang ingin menjadi penerbit dan pada masa yang sama terdapat kekosongan jawatan penerbit dengan syarat membuat dokumentari pendek mengenai pencak silat namun orang yang ingin di dokumentarikan tidak mahu identitinya didedahkan. Rian beritahu Adif dia nak ke Vietnam urusan kerja. Rian tak mahu jumpa Adif lagi sebab dia dah penat nak layan semua kerenah dan cemburu Adif. Tarikh dua bulan sudah hampir dan ia buatkan Adif susah hati sebab Rian sudah menjauhinya semula. Fitrin tunggu Adif, ugut akan ganggu keluarga jika Adif tak jumpa dia. Adif marah, cekak leher Fitrin. Faisal datang, Adif lepaskan Fitrin dan pergi. Adif memandu laju ke sekolah Farhan, risau sesuatu berlaku. Dia terlanggar tembok selepas mengelak kereta lain. Adif cedera, Rian terkejut dan apabila Rian pulang ke Malaysia, Farhan sudah ikut Adif dan Adif mahu ambil Farhan. Rian mengaku dia salah sangka dan tuduh Adif macam macam. Mereka bergaduh besar sehingga Adif hampir melafazkan cerai tapi Rian cuba merayu.

programme.title: WOK Ep.1 Ep1
programme.desc: Kesihatan Maimun semakin merosot. Luka pada tapak kaki akibat terpijak kaca, semakin teruk. Usop cuba bantu mana yang mampu. Maimun risau akan Wok. Jika dia pergi, siapa yang akan menjaga Wok. Usop, dalam diam menaruh hati, namun ditolak Maimun. Maimun minta tolong Usop untuk carikan lelaki yang sesuai untuk dijadikan suami kepada Wok yang istimewa.

programme.title: WOK Ep.2 Ep2
programme.desc: Maimun masih bekerja keras walau menahan sakit kerana mengenang nasib Wok. Ketika pulang dari berniaga sayur, Maimun dilanggar motorsikal. Kecederaan kaki bertambah teruk. Doktor nasihatkan untuk memotong kaki supaya tidak merebak. Maimun lari keluar dari hospital. Kepenatan dalam melarikan diri dari hospital, sedih mengenangkan dirinya tak mungkin bertahan lama. Dari dibiarkan kaki dipotong, Maimun berharap nyawanya diambil terus. Keesokkannya, usop datang menjenguk dan terkejut, Maimun sudah di pondok usang mereka. Usop seloroh, dia boleh jagakan Wok. Maimun menolak. Kalau boleh nak yang elok. Sebab dia tak nak Wok susah. Cukuplah lalui susah sepanjang menjadi anaknya. Untuk berkahwin dan mencari suami biarlah yang senang sikit dan boleh memberikan kebahagian untuk Wok. Usop senyum kelat. Dia namakan beberapa kenalan. Bolehlah kalau nak dijodohkan. Maimun teruja gembira. Pertemuan dengan Deris mengimbau tentang kenakalan mereka berdua dahulu. Masing-masing sudah berubah dan cuci kaki. Tidak lagi terjebak dengan dadah.

programme.title: WOK Ep.3 Ep3
programme.desc: Maimun masih berpendirian tetap untuk tidak menjodohkan Usop dengan anaknya Wok. Dia yakin, Usop akan kembali seperti Usop yang dulu. Maimun tak nak Wok menjadi mangsa kemudian hari. Deris tidak diterima oleh masyarakat sekeliling. Banyak yang memandang serong. Sehinggakan dirinya dipukul dan dihalau. Dia masih berdiam diri dan membiarkan segala perbuatan jahat manusia terhadap dirinya. Pertemuan dengan penjual bunga di pasar iaitu jirannya sendiri Suria membuka mata Deris bahawa ada juga yang prihatin. Suria pula, terlebih perasan dan beranggapan tentu Deris menyimpan perasaan terhadap dirinya. Maimun teringin membeli bantal kekabu. Nak dijadikan hadiah, kalau-kalau Wok akan berumah tangga, tetapi duit tidak mencukupi. Penemuan Usop dengan Deris telah memberi idea untuk perkenalkan Deris dengan Wok. Sebagai calon suami yang dikira cocok mengikut kriteria Maimun. Pada masa sama, Usop masih berharap Maimun sudi menerima dirinya untuk memperisterikan Wok yang istimewa.

programme.title: WOK Ep.4 Ep4
programme.desc: Pelawaan Usop untuk memperisterikan Wok masih ditolak Maimun. Usop ambil mudah dan memperkenalkan Deris sebagai calon sesuai untuk Wok kerana Deris tidak tinggal solat dan sebagainya. Akhirnya selesai majlis pernikahan Wok di pejabat agama. Sekejap sahaja segalanya berubah. Wok dibawa pulang ke rumah Deris dan janji Deris akan selalu membawa Wok pulang. Setelah seminggu berlalu, batang hidung mereka belum lagi kelihatan. Disangkakan malam pertama penuh bahagia, tersiksa dibalik pintu yang begitu asing bagi diri Wok. Keadaan kesihatan Maimun merundum akibat terseliuh dekat depan rumah. Maimun masih menantikan anak yang satu untuk pulang melawatnya. Menunggu dan terus menunggu.

programme.title: WOK Ep.5 Ep5
programme.desc: Wok disiksa suami sendiri, disiksa batin dan fizikal kerana nafsu binatangnya. Maimun semakin tenat dan akhirnya menghembuskan nafas seorang diri di rumah dalam keadaan menanti kepulangan Wok. Usop yang mulanya enggan menghulurkan bantuan, tidak tergamak dan membawa Maimun ke hospital. Memandangkan keadaan Maimun amat teruk dan dia memilih untuk menghembuskan nafas terakhir di rumah. Maimun dibawa pulang. Segalanya atas bantuan Usop. Sampai dibandar, Usop sedaya upaya menjejaki Wok. Akhirnya Usop dapat bertemu dengan Deris. Wok dapat melepaskan diri, apabila Deris lalai kerana kelam kabut keluar rumah tanpa mengunci mangga pintu. Wok berjaya keluar dari rumah Deris dengan kudrat yang ada.

programme.title: Kahwin 5
programme.desc: Kahwin 5 berkisarkan tentang seorang usahawan mangkuk plastik (dari Perak) yang berjaya, Dr K (Usop Wilcha) yang sudah memenuhi kuota 4 isteri dari 4 negeri berbeza iaitu Saadiah dari Selangor (Dian P Ramlee), Sahara dari Kelantan (Adrea Abdullah), Monalisa dari Negeri Sembilan (Norish Karman) dan Mimi dari Sabah (Marsha Milan). programme.desc: Menunggu kepulangan anak yang tak kunjung tiba, Maimun meninggal dunia tanpa sesiapa disisinya. Tersiksa batin dan seluruh isi jiwa Maimun, begitu juga Wok yang disiksa bagai patung tak bernyawa. Deris menunjukkan dirinya yang sebenar. Kaki seks, kaki dera fizikal dan mental. Usop cuba dapatkan Wok dengan mencari Deris. Personaliti Deris sudah mulai terbongkar. Dia tidak endah mengenai pemergiaan Maimun. Betapa kejamnya Deris, tidak langsung membawa Wok balik untuk melihat arwah Maimun untuk kali terakhir. Wok disiksa teruk dan tekad dan cuba membunuh Deris.

programme.title: WOK Ep.7 Ep7
programme.desc: Wok terus didera, diikat. Sesekali dilayan seperti hamba abdi. Deris semakin lupa daratan. Usop sedih dengan apa yang terjadi dan masih belum dapat mencari Wok. Paling sedih, bila Wok tidak dapat melawat Jenazah Maimun buat kali terakhir. Deris mula mendapat selera baru. Cuba menlanggani Wani, budak yang baru berjinak-jinak menjadi call girl. Paling sedih, Wani adalah adik Alai. Deris ditangkap atas tudugan merogol dan mengakibatkan kematian kepada Ita, bekas kekasih Alai. Wok terus dikurung, permintaan jiran untuk melihat Wok membuatkan Deris buntu. Alai sedaya upaya menjaga Wani supaya tidak jadi seperti arwah kekasihnya.

programme.title: WOK Ep.8 Ep8
programme.desc: Usop dipaksa untuk mencari Wok yang masih belum ditemui. Mekton turut dilanda kerisauan mengenai keberadaan Wok. Paling menyedihkan, Usop sebenarnya telah bertemu dengan Deris pertemuan yang berakhir dengan pergaduhan. Namun begitu, Usop pula yang dituduh cuba mengganggu rumah tangga Deris. Peluang untuk mengetahui lokasi rumah Deris juga terlepas begitu sahaja. Buat pertama kalinya, Deris membawa Wok keluar rumah. Namun, kesan lebam yang masih kelihatan pada wajah Wok membuatkan Deris risau apabila mereka terserempak dengan Suria. Bagi menyembunyikan keadaan Wok, Deris membelikannya niqab. Sementara itu, adik Alai, Wani, baru mula terjerumus ke dalam dunia gelap sebagai call girl. Tanpa disedari sesiapa, Deris berkemungkinan menjadi pelanggan pertamanya. Selepas Deris memperlakukan Wok dengan kasar, dia dalam perjalanan untuk bertemu Wani. Pada masa yang sama, Alai terdengar suara samar-samar dari sebalik pintu rumah Deris dan cuba untuk membukanya...

programme.title: WOK Ep.9 Ep9
programme.desc: Wok akhirnya berjaya melarikan diri dari rumah Deris dengan bantuan Alai. Tempat yang paling selamat buat dirinya kini adalah di masjid atau surau ruang yang memberinya ketenangan dan perlindungan. Namun, trauma yang dialami masih membelenggu, membuatkan Wok sukar untuk tampil di khalayak. Sementara itu, Deris semakin teruja untuk mendapatkan Wani, namun dalam diam dia dibayangi rasa bersalah dan ketakutan terhadap balasan Tuhan. Dia berjanji pada dirinya bahawa ini adalah kali terakhir dia melakukan dosa sebesar ini.

programme.title: WOK Ep.10 Ep10
programme.desc: Wok melarikan diri dari surau selepas menyedari ada individu yang cuba menghubungi Deris. Dalam masa yang sama, Suria menghubungi ibu bapa Ros untuk memaklumkan situasi sebenar. programme.title: Colombiana
programme.desc: Pada tahun 1992, di Bogota, Colombia, baron dadah Don Luis Sandoval menghantar penguatkuasanya Marco dan sekumpulan lelaki bersenjata untuk membunuh rakan sekutunya Fabio Restrepo dan keluarganya kerana Fabio telah menentangnya dengan cuba meninggalkan kehidupan jenayahnya. Fabio memberikan anak perempuannya yang berusia sembilan tahun, Cataleya, kad memori komputer SmartMedia yang dimuatkan dengan maklumat mengenai perniagaan Don Luis dan memberitahunya itu adalah "pasport"nya; dia juga memberikan alamat bapa saudaranya Emilio di Chicago, yang akan menjaganya. Akhirnya, dia meninggalkannya dengan kalung orkid cataleya ibunya. Selepas Fabio dan isterinya Alicia ditembak mati, Cataleya melarikan diri dan mencari suaka di Kedutaan A.S. Dia diberikan laluan ke Amerika Syarikat selepas menyerahkan kad memori kepada kakitangan kedutaan. Walaupun pegawai Amerika cuba memindahkannya ke dalam sistem jagaan angkat, Cataleya menjejaki bapa saudaranya di Chicago dan memintanya melatihnya sebagai pembunuh.

programme.title: Grace
programme.desc: Selepas kehilangan anak yang dikandungnya, Madeline Matheson berkeras untuk membawa bayi itu hingga haid. Selepas penghantaran, kanak-kanak itu secara ajaib kembali hidup dengan selera untuk darah manusia. Madeline berdepan dengan keputusan muktamad seorang ibu.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Lokman mahu mengadakan majlis tari-menari bertopeng untuk mencipta imej positif buat syarikat insuransnya. Memandangkan Leo juga akan hadir, Sofia meyakinkan Black untuk menghadiri majlis tari-menari itu bersamanya, dan ini mendorong Black untuk belajar menari. Tetapi ketika berada di majlis itu, dia ternampak Sofia dan Lokman menari bersama dan timbul rasa cemburu, satu emosi yang asing buat dirinya. Sementara itu, Aisya menerima panggilan misteri daripada telefon Black semasa perjalanannya ke lapangan terbang. Pemanggil misteri itu memberitahu Aisya bahawa nyawa Malik dalam bahaya melainkan dia hadir di majlis tari-menari bertopeng itu. Berjayakah Black menangkap 419 akhirnya atau adakah pembunuh upahan itu dapat menghalang Black dan mengucar-ngacirkan misinya? Kalau Black kehilangan tubuh Malik, dia juga akan kehilangan Sofia, wanita manusia yang telah menyentuh hatinya...

Selain itu, Mak Cik Vi menjadi curiga apabila McCall ponteng keluar pada malam keluarga lain untuk bekerja.

Walaupun Melati berharap peluang kedua akan menjadikan dia lelaki yang lebih baik, Watih masih tidak mempercayai Sigit. Dia memberi amaran kepadanya bahawa jika dia bertindak menentang Melati dan keluarganya, dia mempunyai kuasa untuk merobek jiwanya dari tubuh barunya. Sara, seorang detektif polis dari bandar dan rakan keluarga Fadil bimbang tentang dia selepas radionya senyap dan memutuskan untuk menjelajah ke negara itu untuk memastikan dia baik-baik saja. Dia membunuh Watih, membalas dendam pertamanya.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assasin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code Patuhi misi. Jangan alihkan pandangan dari sasaran. Jangan tunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh untuk mencari tahu siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Ketika dia semakin hampir membongkar rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan korupsi, dia dikhianati dalam satu tugas, menjadikannya sasaran dan membahayakan orang yang disayanginya. Kini, dikhianati dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling berbahaya, Natee mengikut kod baru Jadi lebih pantas, lebih kuat, serang lebih ganas, dan bertahan hidup. Filem ini diarahkan oleh Panna Rittikrai, koreografer aksi Ong Bak dan mentor kepada bintang aksi Tony Jaa, yang kembali bekerjasama dengan Dan Chupong dari filem Born to Fight (2004) dalam filem terakhirnya.

Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

Dia dibuli oleh kawan-kawannya, ibunya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan lelaki lain, dan gadis yang dia cintai mengkhianati lelaki lain. Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.desc: Nabila dan Amry mendapati mereka tidak lagi mengingati mimpi mereka apabila mereka terjaga daripada tidur. Namun, mereka mula mengalami deja vu yang membuatkan mereka teringat satu sama lain.

Selain itu, pelajaran memandu Delilah membawa McCall dan Aunt Vi untuk mengajarnya satu pelajaran yang lebih besar tentang tanggungjawab peribadi.

programme.title: Bloody Hell
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki dengan masa lalu yang penuh misteri melarikan diri ke luar negara untuk melepaskan diri daripada neraka peribadinya namun akhirnya tiba di sebuah tempat yang jauh lebih mengerikan.

programme.title: Sepasang Kurung Biru
programme.desc: Sarina kembali menjejakkan kaki ke rumah bekas suaminya, Azran, setelah lima tahun mereka berpisah. Azran masih menyimpan rasa kasih dan berharap ada peluang untuk menyulam kembali cinta yang terlerai. Namun, kepulangan Sarina tidak disambut mesra oleh anak mereka, Sue, yang masih menyimpan luka. Bagi Sue, ibunya adalah wanita kejam yang pergi meninggalkan dia dan ayahnya untuk berkahwin dengan lelaki lain.

programme.title: Tuan Badol
programme.desc: Seorang yang sangat garang tetapi rupa-rupanya takut dengan isteri, itulah Ibrahim. Seorang Pengurus Besar, dia mempunyai seorang pembantu rumah bernama Nor. Tuan Badol jatuh cinta terhadap Nor apabila melakukan lawatan ke tanah miliknya. Pelbagai cara telah dicubanya untuk memikat Nor, seorang yang hidup serba sederhana di tanah perkampungan setinggan miliknya.

programme.title: Tragedi Oktober
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan Wati dan Syamsul yang telah berkahwin selama enam tahun dan mempunyai seorang anak lelaki bernama Shamin. Kebahagiaan mereka tergugat apabila Syamsul terlibat dalam satu tragedi, menyebabkan Wati menjadi balu. Awie, bekas kekasih Wati, mula mendekati semula selepas bertemu secara tidak sengaja, meskipun dia kini sedang menjalinkan hubungan dengan Farah, anak seorang hartawan. Hubungan mesra yang terjalin kembali antara Wati dan Awie menimbulkan ketegangan dengan Farah, yang cemburu dan menuduh Wati cuba merampas Awie semula. Awie kemudiannya bertunang dengan Farah demi meyakinkan cintanya, namun konflik berlarutan dan berakhir dengan sebuah tragedi yang menyayat hati.

programme.title: Fenomena
programme.desc: Isabella yang menghidapi penyakit aneh ketika berusia setahun pulang semula ke Terengganu dengan harapan penyakitnya itu dapat dirawat. Hanya mempunyai masa enam bulan lagi untuk hidup, Isabella tekad untuk pulang mencari penawar. Berpendapat bahawa seorang dukun, Labib sahaja yang mampu mengubatinya - dia tekad ingin pulang mencarinya.

programme.title: Terbakar Di Hati
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Badrul, seorang usahawan berjaya yang ingin berkahwin lagi kerana isterinya, Rozi, tidak mampu memberikannya zuriat meskipun mereka telah berkahwin selama sepuluh tahun. Rozi kemudian dihalau keluar apabila tidak bersetuju dengan cadangan suaminya itu. Namun, takdir berubah apabila Rozi disahkan hamil dua bulan, sekali gus menjernihkan kembali hubungan mereka. Kebahagiaan itu bagaimanapun tidak berkekalan setelah anak mereka dilahirkan, bayi tersebut didapati mengalami kecacatan. Badrul yang tidak dapat menerima kenyataan itu mula berasa malu, sehingga sanggup memukul dan melontarkan kata-kata yang mengguris hati isterinya.

programme.title: Gila-Gila Remaja

programme.desc: In a bad economy, many people dream of becoming rich overnight, especially the Jiang family. Mother Jiang pushes her three children to earn money so that they can one day live in luxury. Even her daughter-in-law wishes for the same thing. She hopes that one day she can visit her parents with the money that spills out of her purse.

programme.title: I Corrupt All Cops
programme.desc: Corruption was rampant in the Hong Kong Police Force in 1960s and 70s. Chief Inspector Lak launders drug money with three other police officers, and a young officer from the newly established Independent Commission Against Corruption division is determined to bring them down.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: Cliff Walkers
programme.desc: The first spy thriller movie by famous Director Zhang Yi Mou, this film follows four Communist Party special agents who embark on a secret operation in the Japanese puppet state of Manchukuo in 1932. Sold out by a traitor, the agents, who split up into two teams, find themselves surrounded by threats on all sides. Can they complete their mission?

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: CJ7
programme.desc: Stephen Chow returns in this hilarious and heartwarming tale of a father and son who discover an adorable alien in the trash.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Song of Spring
programme.desc: An 85-year-old mother lives with her 65-year-old daughter who is suffering from Alzheimer's disease, causing her to suffer a decline in memory, mental confusion and disorientation. Though the elderly mother has to shoulder the burden of a caregiver, she still wants to be with her daughter forever.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tungs mad fate?

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a persons subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma

programme.title: Customs Frontline
programme.desc: After boarding an unauthorized cargo ship and finding its entire crew dead, the Hong Kong Customs officers uncover a hidden cache of illegal weapons linked to an international conflict. As Customs officer Zhou Zheng Li and Interpols Ying go undercover, they unveil a multinational operation with ties closer to home.

programme.title: Shining for One Thing
programme.desc: Zhang Wan Sen plans to confess his crush on Lin Bei Xing after the college entrance exam, but an accident changes everything tragically. As Zhang feels helpless and devastated, he fortuitously travels back in time with Lin before the accident happens. Can he make amends and convey his regrets this time?

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: In Broad Daylight
programme.desc: Based on a true event of a news investigative unit receiving a tip-off about the abuse of residents in an Elderly and Disabled Care Home. To expose the homes wrongdoings, reporter Kay goes undercover to expose the inhumanity and unveil the cruel truth under broad daylight.

programme.title: God of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers"; clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Undercover Hidden Dragon
programme.desc: In this hilarious comedy, Fat is a gangster who suffers from amnesia. Believing that he is actually an undercover policeman, Fat attempts to arrest gang leader Big Bro, but instead becomes the gangsters best ally. To complicate matters further, a gangster named Wind, who looks exactly like Fat, starts a turf war with Big Bro.

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: The Unwavering Brotherhood
programme.desc: The revered elder of a triad gang faces succession uncertainty when his three trusted underlingsHua, Fei, and Guoare robbed while transporting gang money. Determined to redeem himself, Hua vows to track down the robbers. However, when Hua discovers that Fei and Guo are connected to the robbery, he must choose between loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Singing Killer
programme.desc: Chiang Yi is blackmailed into a jewelry heist by his former boss, who threatens to expose his shady past. Complications arise when he discovers his first love works at the store.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Baos chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Police Force
programme.desc: A man joins the Hong Kong police force to track down a murderer who has killed his friend in a robbery. While he struggles to reconcile his law defending police duty with his desire for vengeance, he also has a new-found respect for the law.

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: Return Of The Dead
programme.desc: A long-awaited horror sequel after Enchanted Shadow, this is about three asylum inmates telling their stories. In story one, a husband and wife discover they should be careful what they wish for. A naked female ghost seeks revenge from her watery grave in story two, and a dead prostitute returns as a ghost in the last tale.

programme.title: Challenge of the Masters
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung must prove himself worthy to be taught by Master Lu, who was also his fathers martial arts teacher. Although he is defeated in a competition, Wong Fei Hungs passion in Kung Fu finally moves Lu and allows him to become Lus disciple.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: My Rebellious Son
programme.desc: A corrupt official attempts to steal a priceless Buddha statue from a temple to please a group of Westerners. Luckily, Doctor Zhang and his son manage to defeat the Western boxers, the Japanese Kendo opponents and the Western longsword fighters with Chinese kung fu, thus saving the Buddha statue.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.

programme.title: Two Champions of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: Yu Lou is betrayed by his wife and eventually killed by her lover, Fung, who is the boss of a martial arts school. Yu Lous brother, Xiao Lou, knows about his tragic death and is determined to take revenge for him.

programme.title: The Tiger and the Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and youve got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain, and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and youve got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: The Sword Stained with Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yongs novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: Cat VS Rat
programme.desc: Zhan and Bai are equally matched in martial arts skills. Bai saves the Emperor one day but did not believe in his identity and rejects a promotion. When Zhan is promoted to the royal guard after saving the Emperor, Bai gets angry and tries to prank him by stealing the imperial jade seal. Luckily, Zhan is able to retrieve the seal with his skills.

programme.title: The Land of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women only give birth to baby girls and do so by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Diary of a Lady-killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: The 36th Chamber of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandmas pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chiefs daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Savanna - The African savanna is an epic landscape, and whether its head-bashing hippos, hormone-crazed elephants or dueling lions, battles that rage on the savanna are just as epic.

programme.title: Wild Tales from the Farm S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Great Escape - Experience life on the farm as things heat up for summer. Watch animals swelter in a rare heatwave, try to stay cool in the nearby freshwater stream, and stash supplies for fall.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Wombat S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Wombat Wood - In the cool highlands near Australias Snowy Mountains is Wombat Wood. There, dotted amongst the trees and dense foliage, are over a hundred wombat burrows. But when some of the burrows are flooded, the wombats need to find safety.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep1
programme.desc: A Tale of Two Penguins - At the waters edge a brave group of male penguins gather, preparing to make the dangerous journey ashore. With many threats ahead, there is safety in number and these petite penguins have important business to attend. Its time to breed and they must find a burrow before the females arrive.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Untamed West - New Zealands West Coast is like nowhere else on Earth. From glacier-covered mountains to rain-drenched native forests to rough frigid seas, the landscape defies belief. Isolated from the rest of the world, this strip of almost untouched wilderness hides a host of endemic animals. Evolutionary castaways, every one of them is a rare ecological jewel. From alpine parrots and shy penguins to mammal-like kiwis and ancient eels. To survive the conditions the wildlife here has to be hardy, cunning and resourceful. A journey along the West Coast reveals the beauty of this land, and the trials and tribulations of the wildlife that live here.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Wild Fortresses - In New Zealand, two wild fortresses protect the vulnerable native animals: One a remote island protected by a moat of saltwater, the other a hilltop citadel surrounded by a predator-proof barrier. This is the story of these delicate sanctuaries and the life that thrives within them.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Ocean Legacy - Spring on New Zealands east coast is a time of promise for the New Zealand Fur Seal and the Norther Royal Albatross. Theyve returned to their land to breed. But harsh terrain, fickle weather and hungry predators will conspire to make lives difficult for them. Only the strongest will survive to carry forward their legacy.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Creepiest Crawlies - New Zealands isolated islands are famed as an unusual paradise, home to a variety of unique wildlife. Best known for its flightless birds, ancient reptiles and coastal mammals, a closer look reveals another world. A land of miniature monsters, Lilliputian predators and tiny terrors that lead remarkable lives, where every hunter is also the hunted and survival is always a giant struggle. Journey into the undergrowth and discover life on a different scale. From giant carnivorous centipedes and nocturnal crickets to fishing spiders and glowing worms with silken traps. Weird and wonderful, these unsung heroes are Wildest New Zealands Creepiest Crawlies.

programme.title: Waterworld Africa S1 Ep6
programme.desc: The Chobe River - A mighty river snakes through wilderness in southern Africa. Its vast flood plains are a magnet for animals that, during the dry season, travel great distances to reach this oasis. But every animal has its place along the banks of the mighty Chobe.

programme.title: Waterworld Africa S1 Ep7
programme.desc: Source to Sea - Follow a rivers epic quest to find the ocean, carrying water that has floated high over the mountains, quenched giant thirsts, and cut through rock, only to spill its nutrients into the warm and vibrant Indian Ocean and continue its endless cycle.

programme.title: Waterworld Africa S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Wetland Wonder - South Africas greatest wetland, Lake St. Lucia, provides sustenance for animals that depend on standing water, including hippos, crocs, and countless water birds. But during a drought, the system faces challenges that have devastating consequences.

programme.title: Loons: A Cry from the Mist
programme.desc: Race the clock with biologists as they try to figure out why North American loons are suddenly in danger. Unlock the mysterious lives of these beloved birds, and ponder whether their cries will continue to be summers soundtrack or go silent forever.

programme.title: Baboons: Rules of the Troop
programme.desc: Follow four families of four different species - the resourceful Beach Troop, the warlike Desert Troop, the disciplined River Troop, and the peaceful Mountain Band - to find out why these primates are among the most successful animals in Africa.

programme.title: Supersenses S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Super Sight - Vision its how ninety-five percent of animals interpret the world. Every species on Earth is a chapter in the fascinating story of sight. This episode follows that story from blurry beginnigs to mind-blowing hexnocular vision.

programme.title: Supersenses S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Super Powers - See the animals that push the limits of physics, chemistry and engineering to pull off feats that humans can only dream of, and find out how evolution granted them with such amazing abilities. Sometimes it takes a super-power just to survive.

programme.title: Supersenses S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Invisible World - Dive into a dazzling world beyond human perception, where animals use their super senses to detect light we cant see, sound we cant hear and even stranger forces we cant begin to detect.

programme.title: Alien Abyss S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Origin Stories - Get acquainted with an array of ocean oddballs and learn how billions of years worth of changes, from ice ages to asteroid strikes, have shaped their looks and skills. Meet blind worms who fish, walking sharks, tree-climbing crabs, and much more.

programme.title: Alien Abyss S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Allies and Adversaries - Feel the love in the strange-but-heartwarming partnerships between some of Earths oddest creatures. Dive deep to see strange animals, from snapping shrimp to wolf eels, offer a hand to their fellow ocean-going weirdos to ensure mutual survival.

programme.title: Alien Abyss S1 Ep3
programme.desc: The Next Generation - Channel your inner sci-fi fan and explore the bizarre mating rituals of the oceans most peculiar creatures. Learn how bloody battles for mates, gender bending and supersize litters of babies just might secure a next generation for these animals.

programme.title: The Ocean's Greatest Feast
programme.desc: Get a front-row seat to the planets biggest biomass migration, the annual 1,000-mile sardine run along South Africas east coast. See billions of these tiny fish run a gauntlet of hungry predators, including stealthy seals and dive-bombing gannets.

programme.title: Wild Tales from the Farm S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Change in the Air - Watch life on the farm adjust as the leaves start to turn, from the sheep whose woolly coats keep them warm during the first frost to the bees that feed on the last bit of nectar before hibernation.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Wombat S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Joey's Journey - Wombats are solitary, slow-moving creatures, but breeding time brings out their energy, aggression and lots of play. Meet a southern hairy-nosed wombat named Birri, whos trying to find a mate, along with a female named Winnie and her joey, Fred.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Haven of Giants - Lewa Conservancy is working to return elephants to territory from Mt. Kenya to Samburu National Park. They've also created an elephant exclusion zone to try and restore a damaged ecosystem. Radio tracking collars are used for both initiatives to help conservationists better understand the elephants needs - and to see if they're returning to their natural corridors.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Ivory Wars - Elephant hunting has been banned in Kenya for 40 years. Organized gangs of armed poachers are still targeting elephants, illegally hunting them and selling their ivory tusks on the black market. Environmentalists and conservationists are sounding the alarm.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Horses of the Sun - Grvys zebras population has dropped by 50% in less than 20 years. Environmentalists say that if we arent vigilant, they could disappear all together. Lewa Conservancy is at the heart of efforts to protect the species so that they can replenish their numbers

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Vanishing Wilderness - Kenya's growing human population is taking land and resources away from wildlife. The squeeze is creating increasing numbers of conflicts between humans and animals, and is one of the biggest issues in African conservation.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries S1 Ep5
programme.desc: A Place in the Wild - Kenya takes a major step with the opening of its first community-run rhino sanctuary in the heart of Samburu territory. The threat to Kenyas rhinos from armed, illegal poaching gangs is the highest it's been in 40 years, which makes the sanctuary vital.

programme.title: Land of Primates S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Lemurs of Anja Mountain - Millions of years ago, castaway creatures were stranded on the rugged shores of Madagascar. Left to evolve on their own, theyve found a way to perfectly adapt to their tropical climate. Now, see what life is like for a family of ring-tailed lemurs.

programme.title: Land of Primates S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Lemurs of Madagascar - The island is the land of Lemurs. Lemurs are fascinating arboreal primitive primates of Madagascar represented in all sizes, colors, and shapes from the largest Indri to the tiny mouse lemur.

programme.title: Land of Primates S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Wanderers of the Lost Forest - Hogsback, South Africa, is home to two fascinating primates: The Samango monkeys and the Cape Parrots. See how they overcome habit loss, travel across town for food, and make the most of a difficult situation.

programme.title: Land of Primates S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Baboons of Bambelela - The Bambelela Troop is a successful and gregarious troop of Chacma Baboons that live in a pristine valley in the Waterberg Mountains of South Africa. But they have a problemtheyre not the only baboons around.

programme.title: Land of Primates S1 Ep5
programme.desc: The Geladas of Ethiopia - The gelada is a rare monkey that lives in the Simien Mountains of Ethiopia. Theyre charismatic, vocal, and mix affection and confrontation. Watch as they face the challenges of their habitatand each other.

programme.title: In for the Kill

They'd 'found' Fuse's Special Things and taken them to start a collection of their own.
